title: DuBose, Wolverines bite Wolfson in district contest
text:
DuBose, Wolverines bite Wolfson in district contest 
Sat, Oct 24, 2015 @ 12:23 am 
The Times-Union 
WESTSIDE 40 
WOLFSON 6 
Amari DuBose rushed for three TDs in Westside’s rout of winless Wolfson (0-9, 0-3 District 4-5A). ... Tahveon Nicholson added a 63-yard touchdown rush for the Wolverines (3-6, 2-2). ... Westside’s Ancoren Oliver (80 yards) and Jojo Collins (20 yards) returned interceptions for touchdowns.
